<br>
<br>
Greetings,<br>
GM-Darcfae (Karana Admin) asked me to post this here to avoid further exploits.<br>
<br>
There is a known bug in the East Commonlands tunnel, at the Shady. Near Bubar, along the wall, there is a fire pot. DO NOT ACCEPT ANY TRADES FROM OR TO SOMEONE STANDING ON THIS FIRE POT OR BEHIND !<br>
<br>
The flames are &quot;non receptive objects&quot;. ie you will NOT receive &quot;confirm drop&quot; box, nor trade windows. On sunday, I had a 50Kpp trade, the platinum simply drops on the ground, the scammer (in this case : [DELETED]) takes them and goes &lt;LinkDead&gt;.<br>
<br>
So please be VERY careful regarding this situation, so that it will not happen again (until VI fixes this).<br>
<br>
